Title: Science
Presenters: The Future of Healthcare in the 21st Century and Beyond
Book Description: Amara Sugalski, Catherine Shaffer, Jessica Roland
All Day Event: 'Movies and Sci-fi TV shows present visions of the future of medicine that may or may not come to pass. How will hospitals and healthcare providers step up to meet the challenges in today's health care? What are the future challenges? What roles will genomics and neuroscience play? Our panelists explore these themes in a wide ranging discussion with audience participation.'
